# ================== Ester Hybrid Search — ENV presety (primer) ==================
# A/B-slot gibridnogo poiska:
#   A — passthrough: ispolzovat tekuschiy dense-poisk kak est.
#   B — ansambl: coarse (BM25/ierarkhicheskiy) + dense (vektor) s lineynym smeshivaniem.
HYBRID_SEARCH_AB=A

# Ves dense v ansamble (0..1). 0.55 — plotnyy sloy chut vazhnee coarse.
HYBRID_ALPHA=0.55

# Skolko kandidatov brat iz coarse-poiska dlya doranzhirovaniya dense.
HYBRID_COARSE_LIMIT=50

# Mosty:
# - Yavnyy: (Infoteoriya ↔ Inzheneriya) upravlenie ensemble bez pravki koda.
# - Skrytyy #1: (Kibernetika ↔ Resursy) ogranichenie pula kandidatov.
# - Skrytyy #2: (Memory ↔ Poisk) stabilnost kontraktov dlya RAG.

# Zemnoy abzats: eto «regulyatory na smesitele» — kakoy potok schitat glavnym i skolko kandidatov podmeshivat.

# c=a+b
